  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Serbia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project &quot;Raising awareness among primary and secondary school students on climate change and energy efficiency problems with a simultaneous capacity building of Ecological education and sustainable development centre&quot; would be divided up into two phases. The first phase refers to the climate change phenomenon in general and has as a goal the pupils to get familiarized with the problems relating to climate change and their solving. The goal of the second phase is to point to the advantages of rational energy use, the relevance it has for our environment and to bring it in relation with the global issue, i.e. climate changes.Overall objective of the project is raising environmental awareness of pupils and citizens on climate change and energy efficiency and connecting these two problems (cause and effect).</narrative>
  </description>
